  "instructions": [
    "Soak the cashews in water for at least an hour before use.",
    "In a pan, sauté garlic cloves in olive oil until golden brown. Add chopped tomatoes and cook until softened.",
    "Blend soaked cashews with flour, water, salt, and cinnamon powder into a creamy base.",
    "Stir in the tomato mixture and simmer for about 10 minutes to thicken slightly.",
    "Sauté diced tomatoes briefly before adding them to the creamy base.",
    "Fold in fresh parsley and basil leaves to garnish the dish."
